tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE player_interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id UUID,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE player_interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    duration_seconds INT
);

CREATE TABLE game_design_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT NOT NULL,
    feedback_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    satisfaction_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE player_interactions ( 
  player_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50), 
  interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
  game_session_id UUID, 
  interaction_data JSONB 
);

CREATE TABLE player_sessions ( 
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
  player_id UUID, 
  start_timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
  end_timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
  session_duration INTERVAL 
);

CREATE TABLE game_design ( 
  game_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
  game_name VARCHAR(100), 
  designer_id UUID, 
  release_date DATE, 
  game_genre VARCHAR(50) 
);

CREATE TABLE PlayerInteractions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id UUID NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    interaction_details JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE PlayerProfiles (
    player_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    player_age INTEGER,
    player_country VARCHAR,
    player_level INTEGER
);

CREATE TABLE GameSessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    session_start TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    session_end TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    player_id UUID NOT NULL,
    game_id UUID NOT NULL
);
